  "elapsed_s": 237.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It has happened here too, right?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in America, it wasn't like it was in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That meant concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I put down that for that reason we request that we could stay in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A week-- within the week, we were let go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But both of us, my brother and I, get a piece of paper that said that within five days we have to leave Belgium proper.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they didn't deport us, but they gave us what they called a further route.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Get out.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the League of Nation agreement that was signed, if you're a political refugee, you're only political refugee, asylum has to be given to you only in the first country that you enter.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If I leave Belgium and I go to France or Holland, it's not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then I'm just a stateless person that can be deported to any other country or back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
